  <LRE_Drug_CondensingEnergyUniversePill.label>【一品】凝气乾坤丹</LRE_Drug_CondensingEnergyUniversePill.label>
  <!-- EN: First-rate Pill, After consumption, the spiritual energy stored within the elixir will be released and enter the dantian of the user, replenishing all spiritual energy, and altering the structure of the user's dantian. This allows for automatic storage of spiritual energy without the need for cultivation. -->
